13:40.240 --> 13:41.720
and people run after them,

13:41.880 --> 13:45.280
they like to go on working out that yarn

13:45.440 --> 13:49.080
that they have spun for you.

13:50.320 --> 13:55.000
One has to go beyond this mind to feel the spirituality.

13:55.160 --> 13:58.760
With this mind, that is human mind, you cannot understand it,

13:58.920 --> 14:00.960
you have to have Divine mind.

14:01.120 --> 14:03.080
But once you get your realization

14:03.240 --> 14:05.680
your mind also gets enlightened,

14:05.840 --> 14:10.160
and when your mind is enlightened, you can perceive,

14:10.320 --> 14:13.960
penetrate into every situation

14:14.120 --> 14:20.440
in such a deeper manner and the way you can improve it.

14:20.600 --> 14:23.800
I can tell you a simple analogy to understand.

14:23.960 --> 14:31.760
Supposing you are standing in the sea and the sea is rough,

14:31.920 --> 14:35.040
you are afraid of the waves, very much afraid.

14:35.200 --> 14:38.680
But supposing somebody puts you on the boat,

14:38.840 --> 14:42.800
and then you can see those waves and enjoy them.

14:42.960 --> 14:45.280
But supposing you learn how to swim

14:45.440 --> 14:48.080
then you can jump in and save them.

14:48.240 --> 14:50.360
It is not any brainwashing

14:50.520 --> 14:54.840
or any sort of a bombardment of words,

14:55.000 --> 14:57.760
but it is something that happens to you.

14:57.920 --> 15:01.360
You become something as you have become human beings,

15:01.520 --> 15:03.640
you become realized souls

15:03.800 --> 15:09.640
as a result of this last breakthrough of your evolution.

15:09.800 --> 15:12.560
This is happening everywhere no doubt

15:12.720 --> 15:15.440
and it’s working out very well in,

15:15.600 --> 15:18.840
I think they told me, 62 countries

15:19.000 --> 15:22.280
but at least I know of definitely of 52 countries

15:22.440 --> 15:24.880
where there We have got very strong centers

15:25.040 --> 15:27.760
where it is working out.

15:27.920 --> 15:29.920
Now whatever we are telling you here

15:30.080 --> 15:32.400
you need not accept blindfolded.

15:32.560 --> 15:35.400
