15:49.560 --> 15:52.280
If it works then you have to accept.

15:52.440 --> 15:54.480
If you are honest you have to accept.

15:54.640 --> 15:57.240
If it doesn’t work. If it works with many,

15:57.400 --> 15:59.760
why not try and work it out.

