Most of the people do get their realization. I have seen it.

16:03.240 --> 16:05.040
It’s a wonderful thing that is happening

16:05.200 --> 16:08.200
that masses of people can get realization.

16:08.360 --> 16:12.480
Depends on also certain places like Russia I was amazed.

16:12.640 --> 16:14.360
Where they have not heard the name of God

16:14.520 --> 16:15.920
they have never heard the name of Christ.

